                  "pageId": 712548,
                  "revisionId": 2676657,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Damage redirection only begins at the end of Shadows of the Dead casting animation, when all shadows have spawned and Nekros is visually linked to them."
                }
              }
